title: 1X1 Includes W/S/G & Cable TV
posting_body: ['Welcome to Lacey Park Apartments!', 'Conveniently located near shopping, pharmacy, and food centers, schools, a main bus line, and a trail head, we are tucked back in a park like setting.', 'We are a community of friendly and inclusive people.', "Enjoy such features as a residents' lounge, fitness center, swimming pool, spa, playground and sports court.", 'We include a full size washer and dryer in every unit.', 'Let us pay your water, sewer, garbage, and basic cable for you.', 'Our on-site management and maintenance will meet your needs in a friendly and efficient manner.', 'Call Lacey Park Apartments to help you make us your new home today.', 'Please, contact us at', 'show contact info', 'to obtain our rental criteria.', 'Thank you!', 'APPLY HERE : <URL>', 'Storage units are available for $65 - $75 per month.', 'Carports are available for $25 per month.', 'Garages are available for $125 per month.', 'Please, contact us to obtain our rental criteria.', 'Thank you!', 'YOU MAY APPLY HERE : <URL>']
